{
  "texts": [
    "Parttime income, scholarships/grants, and other sources constitute tiny proportions of the sample.",
    "The cumulative relative frequency indicates that nearly 99% of participants rely on either family support, part-time income, or full-time income as their primary source of financial support.",
    "The data obtained on the Order Frequency as created by the survey is displayed in Figure 5 below.",
    "Figure 5 presents the participants' average weekly food delivery order frequency: Never, 1~2 times, 3~5 times, and More than 5 times.",
    "The data reveal that most participants (50.51%) use food delivery services 1~2 times weekly."
  ]
